<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.0-beta3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-eOJMYsd53ii+scO/bJGFsiCZc+5NDVN2yr8+0RDqr0Ql0h+rP48ckxlpbzKgwra6" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <title>MovieAPI</title>
    <style>
        #heading{
            margin-top: 7rem;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }
        .card {
            padding: 2%;
        }
        form.form-control {
          border: 0;  
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <section id="heading">
        <h1 class="text-center">The MoviesAPI</h1>
    </section>
    
    <section id="body">
        <div class="card" style="width:35rem; margin: 0% auto;">
        	<div class="conatiner justify-center">
        		<p>This is an API that returns recommendations and predicted ratings for each of the recommendations through Collaborative Filtering approach. The model uses the <a href="https://www.kaggle.com/shubhammehta21/movie-lens-small-latest-dataset">MovieLens</a> dataset from Kaggle. The corresponding notebook and webapp code along with the api code base is there on <a href="https://github.com/sabrina-gujral/recommender-system">GitHub</a>
        			<br>
        			Don't forget to look at the main website, <a href="https://shielded-dusk-69513.herokuapp.com/">Dionysus</a></p>
        	</div>
            <form class="form-control" action="/" method="POST">
                <input class="form-control" type="text" placeholder="UserId" name="userId" autocomplete="false" autofocusg/> <br>
                <div class="form-check">
                    <input class="form-check-input" id="re" type="radio" value="re" name="radio" checked/>
                <label class="form-check-label" for="re">Predicted Movies</label>
                </div>
                <div class="form-check">
                <input class="form-check-input" id="ra" type="radio" value="ra" name="radio" />
                <label class="form-check-label" for="ra">Predicted Ratings</label> <br>
                </div>
                <br>
                <button class="btn btn-dark" type="submit">Submit</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <section id="footer">
        <footer class="text-center" style="bottom: 0;">
            <small class="text-secondary">Made by @chilling_adventures</small>
        </footer>
    </section>
    
</body>
</html>